com.fasterxml.clustermate.service.sync

Class SyncListResponse<E extends StoredEntry<?>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fasterxml.clustermate.service.sync.SyncListResponse<E>

  • public class SyncListResponse<E extends StoredEntry<?>>
extends Object
    Simple response POJO used by sync end point; used both for failures (for which message is non-null) and successes (for which entries is non-null.

    NOTE: only used for writing; on reading side we will use a "raw" approach.
